# Enrichment Rules

## Purpose

Enhance signals with additional context before graph insertion.

## Enrichment Types

Signals may be enriched with:

- entity aliases
- geolocation
- narrative classification
- infrastructure mapping

## Techniques

Use deterministic methods:

- NLP pipelines
- entity resolution
- embedding similarity
- knowledge graph traversal

Avoid LLM calls unless strictly necessary.

## Enrichment Timing

Runs after ingestion filtering:


01:00 entity extraction
01:30 enrichment
02:00 graph build


## Output

Enrichment produces:


enriched_signal


which contains:


entities
relationships
narrative cluster
embedding